# Help for ~class~

~class~ shows your inferred DarkPawns class track based on your strongest trained profession and remort path.

## Usage:

  ~class~

## Notes:

- Before remort, your class is inferred from your current skill profile.
- After remort, your remort class path is preserved and shown here.
- Use ~remort~ to view requirements and ~remort confirm~ to remort.
